      "rationale": "At MRL 2 with a commercially validated solver, explicit numerical solver error characterization beyond code verification and GCI is not required. The solver's iterative convergence is monitored via residual drop (> 5 orders of magnitude) and mass imbalance (< 0.01%), which is documented in the simulation log and sufficient for this risk level."
