      "rationale": "Formal model-form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2. The k-omega SST turbulence model is the consensus choice for internal rotating flows in FDA pump guidance. Model-form adequacy is implicitly addressed through the output comparison factor, where agreement within ±15% across all operating points confirms acceptable model form for this COU."
